## Suggested Data Model

### Food Item Example
```js
{
  id: "milk",
  name: "Milk",
  category: "dairy",
  validZones: ["middle_shelf"],
  invalidZones: ["door", "bottom_shelf", "outside"],
  requiresRefrigeration: true,
  explanation: "Milk should stay in a cold, stable part of the fridge, not the door where temperature changes often."
}